<i>Posted by Micheall on 02-02-2002 12:04 AM:</i>

<p><b><img src="images/icons/Cool_Face_Cyan.gif" alt="" width="15" height="15" border="0"> </b></p>

<p>The easiest way to get into Neriak safely is to go to the firepot room in the Timorous Deep, and tp there.  Lands you in a relatively safe spot, near the Foreign Quarter/Neriak Commons zone line.  No guards go there unless pulled.  Still superior camoflauge is a good thing.<br />
<br />
The safest way to get out is with a gate potion, cheapest of course being the Thurg gate potion.  The leatherfoot cap is a close second.<br />
<br />
I've been encouraged to do it, told a 51 ranger can solo the necro guild guards easily and safely once they know the right spot.  I don't yet.<br />
<br />
Yes, I'm considering it.  Going to explore it a bit further for proper hiding spots and pathing with a baby DE alt before I go in.<p><FONT face="arial, helvetica" size="2">__________________<br>
Michealus Cerebrosus, Ranger 52, Tholuxe Paells<br />
